mendations' operation, pointing towards exacerbated load or synchronous call blockages.\n\n4. **CurrencyService**:\n   - Experienced elevated response times, suggesting it may also have been affected by resource constraints or blocked threads.\n\nOverall, the primary cause of the anomaly appears to revolve around the inability of critical services (notably CheckoutService) to handle requests either due to connectivity interruptions or severe internal delays, resulting in failure propagation across related systems."}
